.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Attach to every cell Button inside the detective sheet grid\&. Click once → shows X Click again → clears X State is saved to PlayerPrefs so it persists across sessions\&. 

SETUP: Each cell Button GameObject must have a UNIQUE name, e\&.g: "Cell_Scarlett_Knife", "Cell_Plum_Revolver", etc\&. Each cell needs a child TextMeshProUGUI for the X display\&. 

